Uses of Class
Shapes

    • Uses of Shapes in <Unnamed>

      Subclasses of Shapes in <Unnamed> 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Lines
      The Lines class helps to create line objects so that when a user draws a line onto the drawing panel, their line is able to stay on the panel if the panel were to be minimized.
      class  Rectangles
      * The Rectangles class helps to create line objects so that when a user draws a rectangle onto the drawing panel, their rectangle is able to stay on the panel if the panel were to be minimized.
